'''天主教锡拉库萨总教区'''（{{lang-it|Arcidiocesi di Siracusa}}）是[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]在[[意大利|意大利]][[西西里岛|西西里岛]]东南部设立的一个[[教区|教区]]，1744年升格为总教区，是'''锡拉库萨教省'''的中心<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dsira.html |title=''Catholic Hierarchy'' page |accessdate=2008-10-27 |archive-date=2008-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080105085434/http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dsira.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。锡拉库萨认为自己是[[伯多祿|伯多祿]]在[[安提約基雅|安提約基雅]]之后建立的第2个教会，[[聖保祿|保祿]]在此讲道。

現任總主教為{{link-it|方濟各·洛曼托|Francesco Lomanto}}<ref name="Vatican20200724">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 24.07.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/07/24/200724a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-08-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724155018/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/07/24/200724a.html |archivedate=2020-07-24 |language=en |date=2020-07-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-it|若瑟·科斯坦佐|Giuseppe Costanzo}}和{{link-en|薩維·帕帕拉爾多 (總主教)|Salvatore Pappalardo (archbishop)|薩維·帕帕拉爾多}}<ref name="Vatican20200724" /><ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 12.09.2008 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2008/09/12/0563/01435.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-08-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731121734/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2008/09/12/0563/01435.html |archivedate=2020-07-31 |language=it |date=2008-09-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

